<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="courage-n">courage <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kʌrɪdʒ/    美 /'kɜːrɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-bravery">1.★ <strong>[U] 勇气；胆量；勇敢 (bravery)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>keep up / lose courage
鼓足/失去勇气</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have the courage to do</strong> sth
有勇气做某事</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Saving Private Ryan is an unforgettable anti-war film and also a story of courage and sacrifice.
《拯救大兵瑞恩》是一部令人难忘的反战影片，同时也是一部弘扬大无畏和牺牲精神的故事片。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He would never walk again but he started a new life with great courage.
他再也不能走路了，但是他勇敢地开始了新生活。</p><footer>北师大② – 2</footer></div></div>